\SE[14]T-That was an amazing experience....
\!\SM[nod]\SE[28]Vita, you have the talent to please me....

\SE\SE[0]Oh, could it be that you were playing a shitty
game? \SE[0]Did you make something like before again?

\SE\SE[35]I played.... I had an amazing experience....
\SE[35]I wonder if Laura should give it a try too...?

\SE[5]I-Is it really that amazing...!? \SE[3]Now I'm
curious....

\SE[5]Your appearance hasn't changed from before, huh.
\!\SE[3]Um, this is the controller, right...?

\SE[51] (H-Hey, the real Laura is definitely the real
deal.... \!\SE[23]Ugh... I want to hold you like this, and
squeeze you tight....)

\SE[59] (N-No, stop... Control yourself, Lunaroa. \SE[28]
Right now, Laura is playing a game. \SE[73] You must not
interrupt that experience...!!)

\SE[22]Ah, this time Lunaroa is the main character, huh!
Wow! The enemies are melting away in an instant!
\SE[21]You're really strong after all.... Truly amazing....

\SE[57] (Ah, Laura is controlling my body...? \!\SE[39] Oh
no, isn't that too sensual...?)

\SE[54]...W-What?! Why are there so many mes...!?
\!\SE[51]The mes outside the map are in big trouble...!

\SE[47] (Ah, Laura's heart rate has increased a bit...
\SE[48] Is she sweating a little...? \SE[29] She smells so
good... I can't take it anymore!!)

\SE[26]Huh... What, what...!! \!\SE[54]What's happening to
me right now...!?

\SE[61]Ah... Laura...! Your frightened face is truly
adorable.... \SE[70]Show me more...!! \SE[74]See... You love
this place, don't you...?

\SE[27]Eek! \!\SE[57]W-Wait... I'm currently... playing a
'game'...! \!\SM[tremble]\SE[52]Nn...! No, this is
really...!!

\SE[17] My game has created a sad victim of sexual abuse....
\!\SE[14] Creative works also have these sad aspects,
huh.... \!\SM[nod]\SE[15]... Yeah, it was a good learning
experience.

\SE[19]Ah...! I came up with a great idea...! \!\SE[1]Let's
put it into shape right away...!!

\SE[65]Look... I'm already like this...! \SE[61]Laura really
loves being forced by me, she's such a pervert...!

\SE[23]N-No... don't say it...! \!\SE[46]Ah That place is
off- limits...! \!\SE[52]I, again...!!

Vita was able to grow once again by completing a shitty
game...!

Vita has learned the secret technique \i[1250] To Even
Greater Heights!

I have my own room too... but I might prefer... spending
time here with everyone...

...As for Vega, you see. She drinks a lot of water while
studying... so she ends up going to the bathroom... quite
frequently...

When I look at the flames, my heart becomes calm... The
flames here are the most comforting.
